{"tid":2492811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：第四波疫情明顯受控 同時亦成功阻截變種病毒流入社區","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:02:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cb0a1bb22393a8f6a0d6412265dfda2e470ab8","tid":2492811,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，本港連續3日無發現新型冠狀病毒本地源頭未明個案，認為是一個非常好的跡象，未來本港將採取抗疫新路向。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在記者會說，去年11月下旬以來的第4波疫情明顯受控，過去兩星期的7天移動平均數確診個案為兩宗，源頭未明個案為0.7宗，數字相對非常低，<span class=\"red\">同時亦成功阻截變種病毒流入社區</span>，在第4波疫情的群組，並無引致更大規模的社會爆發，屬可喜現象，她形容香港現時屬低風險地區。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又表示，特區政府在抗疫的能力大大提升，包括檢測、追蹤工作，以及將緊密接觸者送往檢疫。她指出，在第3波疫情，每名確診者平均有2.55名密切接觸者送往檢疫，而第4波疫情有關數字增至3.75人；而在第4波的健身中心群組，155宗確診個案當中，共有約1500人送檢，每名確診者平均有9.7名密切接觸者送往檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585341-20210412.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585341-20210412.htm&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=6c6a078b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585341-20210412.htm&h=fafd1a1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585341-20210412.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你柒婆真係燈神黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ef39c14757d5d5d04ce7b13f17024e2cb0b704","tid":2492811,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85992ba4794de37c252506b3e5da3b39ed0dfe7c","tid":2492811,"uid":51271,"l